{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 653144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "爸妈发音最简单吧应该是", "timestamp": 1606991522, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653146, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得我们那方言就会读f（家乡方言室友完全听不懂那种）", "timestamp": 1606991564, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653149, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "以及方言里的爸妈也不一样", "timestamp": 1606991589, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653151, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "湖南话里面有f发作w的", "timestamp": 1606991638, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653153, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "比如饭读作wan", "timestamp": 1606991659, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653154, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或者是huan?", "timestamp": 1606991672, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653155, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 因为中古汉语无唇齿音", "timestamp": 1606991674, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "(等于没说", "timestamp": 1606991789, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653170, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 看不懂确实哈哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1606991854, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653178, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 唇齿音就是f，v之类的，你用牙齿咬住嘴唇发的", "timestamp": 1606991946, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653179, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 与此对应的是双唇音", "timestamp": 1606991968, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653189, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中古汉语双唇音就四个，b，p，pt，m", "timestamp": 1606992071, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653192, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 那什么时候就产生了唇齿音？或者说现代汉语为什么有？", "timestamp": 1606992101, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653197, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哦中古汉语中间也出现轻唇和重唇分野了", "timestamp": 1606992207, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653199, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 大概唐代以后就出现了", "timestamp": 1606992221, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653205, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "挺有意思的一点是拉丁语也没有唇齿音(轻唇音)", "timestamp": 1606992290, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653222, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这难道不是音韵学的内容，这是音韵学而不是训诂学，语音学，语言类型学也相关，北京大学中文系欢迎您", "timestamp": 1606992610, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653230, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 湘北？", "timestamp": 1606992729, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653264, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 哈哈哈哈是的", "timestamp": 1606993181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653294, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“全世界爸妈发音几乎一样”这句话不太对吧。只是因为中国人接触较多的印欧语系和汉藏语系是这样的，但其实很多语系都不这样发音。比如离我们很近的日语，蒙古语，维语。以及如果cz看清宫剧的话难道不会意识到满语的“阿玛”和“额娘”发音也不是那样吗？", "timestamp": 1606993560, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653310, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 汉藏语系以前也不这么叫", "timestamp": 1606993730, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653348, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 这四个音都是不送气音吗？", "timestamp": 1606994262, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653384, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 汉藏语系以前就是这么叫的，父和母古代的读音就是ba和ma。是因为这两个字的音位移动了才需要再造出爸和妈两个字来代替。与之类似的还有“匍”和“爬”，“怖”和“怕”", "timestamp": 1606994632, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653417, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: pt是送气清音", "timestamp": 1606995027, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653427, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 那不应该是/ph/么", "timestamp": 1606995191, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653429, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 等下，所以中古汉语既有清浊又有送气对立？太可怕了", "timestamp": 1606995236, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653431, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#语言学", "timestamp": 1606995256, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653439, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哦我写错了 我是个辣鸡", "timestamp": 1606995428, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653445, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 什么叫轻唇和重唇分野...\n以及大佬介意留个联系方式方便我请教嘛？邮箱之类的也行", "timestamp": 1606995511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653451, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 是的，清浊对立，送气不送气对立，好在没有送气的浊音(x", "timestamp": 1606995554, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653461, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哦分野就是分开的意思，我看音韵学大佬们都这么用", "timestamp": 1606995626, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653471, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 啊！音韵学大佬？👍", "timestamp": 1606995678, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653484, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有塞音四分的语言，实在不知道是怎么发的", "timestamp": 1606995782, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653487, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 送气浊音还是有的吧我记得，不过至少汉语在内很多语言不存在这类音位了（？）以及这个和清音浊流怎么分啊（", "timestamp": 1606995801, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653491, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 不是大佬，唉，太懒了，没系统学，看了一点点皮毛，门都没入……", "timestamp": 1606995835, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653528, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 对，讲真不知道怎么发音", "timestamp": 1606996094, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653745, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "上古无轻唇音，中古分轻重唇，现在合并完了就剩bpmf。", "timestamp": 1606998367, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653754, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "简单原理可参见《音韵学教程》", "timestamp": 1606998429, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653851, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 608, "w": 1503}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个不是训诂，是音韵。上古只有重唇组帮（p）滂（ph，h表送气，ph即拼音里的p）並（b，浊声母）明（m），中古这四个分化出了非（pf）敷（pfh）奉（bv）微（这个符号打不出来），然后非敷奉的一部分分化出了f", "timestamp": 1606999218, "type": "image", "url": "hh/hhdjd4lkq77iy4qclvv63q276anitxio.jpeg"}, {"cid": 653908, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "爸爸妈妈那个我猜是因为双唇音最好发，两嘴一张不就是了嘛hhhhh", "timestamp": 1606999878, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 654128, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 135048, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 握手", "timestamp": 1607001830, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 135048, "reply": 41, "tag": null, "text": "#学习\n\n语言学门外汉真心请教训诂学大佬\n\n为什么普通话读f音的字，在方言/外语汉源词中经常读p/h？\n\n为什么全世界的父母/爸妈发音几乎都一样？", "timestamp": 1606991469, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1607001831, "url": "", "vote": {}}}